WEBVTT

02:05:03.609 --> 02:05:05.609
If you had kept him
locked in the station...

02:05:05.650 --> 02:05:07.942
the shop keeper wouldn't have
died and Viji won't be in danger!

02:05:08.025 --> 02:05:09.775
Sir, Kumaran is talking the truth.

02:05:09.900 --> 02:05:13.067
Even now, we can delay
his plan and save Viji.

02:05:13.192 --> 02:05:13.900
How?

02:05:14.150 --> 02:05:15.984
A murder has taken place
at Nadhan stores.

02:05:16.025 --> 02:05:17.900
Kumaran has shot the shop keeper.

02:05:17.942 --> 02:05:19.359
We have arrested him at that spot.

02:05:19.359 --> 02:05:20.984
Send a force here, to the spot, at once.

02:05:21.067 --> 02:05:21.567
Over.
